	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habuit hodie dominus <persName>Ioannes Hallerus</persName> sermonem non tam pium quam luculentum eumque ex verbis Christi fere ultimis: „Ite in orbem universum et predicate evangelium omni creaturę“,<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Mk 16, 15.</note> quem omnes boni, presertim eruditi, magnopere laudaverunt.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cumque primitię tam foeliciter ceciderint, spero in recessu fructus hinc uberes.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Voluit quidam<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName>Wolfgang Musculus</persName>; vgl. oben <ref target="file12337">Nr. 2290</ref>, 17-37.</note> ex nostris ecclesię ministris primum de eius vocatione scrupulum quęrere<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>In der Vorlage</hi> quere.</note>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Consules<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName>Jakob Herbrot</persName> und <persName>Hans Welser</persName>.</note> vero durioribus illum verbis docuerunt, quam pie quam que legitime non literis tantum, sed et per me viva voce accersitus sit.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Compescuimus ergo hominem tanquam<pb type="edition" next="657"/> Lutheranę fecis Bucerique progeniem recte.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clamabunt autem <placeName>Witembergenses</placeName>, <placeName>Norinbergenses</placeName> et reliqui eius farinę<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Vgl. Adagia, 3, 5, 44 (<bibl>ASD</bibl> II/5 321f, <ref target="file12491">Nr. 2444</ref>).</note> nos <persName>Zvinglii</persName> dogma ingesturos, concordiam dissipaturos, etc.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scimus quidem<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName>Frölichs</persName> Befürchtungen sollten sich als berechtigt erweisen; s. <hi>Bähler,</hi> <persName>Haller</persName> 10f.</note>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scimus et hoc, puritatem evangelii, non nugas hominum nos sequi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale in eo, qui est unica salus.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">22. novembris 1545.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus G. Lętus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino Henricho suo Bullingero, viro incomparabili, etc<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Vorliegender Brief wie auch die Briefe <ref target="file12334">Nr. 2287</ref>. 2289-2291. 2293. 2295f wurden Bullinger durch <persName>Zwingli d.J.</persName> überbracht; s. oben <ref target="file12337">Nr. 2290</ref>, 57f; unten 2302, 1-9; 2303.</note>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
